        h2
          | How does the licensing work?
        p
          | So basically the music is using the Creative Commons Attribution license. That means you can use my work for your projects, however many times as you want, in any way that you want.
        p
          | As for attribution, its not required for personal work, but if you're making money, I would be honored. For example, if you made a song and uploaded it to iTunes or Spotify. If there's producer credits, you can use "Prod. by Chris Porter".
